{"tid":1629380,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"果d開post話停手又話國際點點點果d撚屌左膠同黑警政府一樣罪大惡極","createTime":"2019-10-06T08:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T19:31:11.000Z","uid":103842,"like":24,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bd4c4f23d428c9e9146e1dc9ebc46f94d5a08c2b","tid":1629380,"uid":103842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:39:50.000Z","msg":"左膠成撚日係度話咩國際輿論轉向 咁樣<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好睇</span></span> 外國人唔知做咩你地搞尻美心 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">會搞到人權法案過唔到</span></span> 不如停下手啦<br />\n我屌你老母仆街左膠 政治BB班 <br />\n你以為美國幫你係真係見你可憐 俾班差佬禁住打所以幫你咩? <br />\n好多地方都有反政府示威啦 印尼 伊拉克 厄瓜多爾 烏克蘭 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">比香港慘多幾十倍 用曬實彈鎮壓 死過百人</span> 有冇見到美國佬幫佢地呀<br />\n美國幫香港係因為有各種政治經濟利益 又可能係用香港制衡中國 否則佢就好似英國佬咁樣 得閒講2句嘴炮就算啦<br />\n既然佢係因為利益幫你 咁會唔會因為你做得唔好睇 因為reddit twitter 少幾個like 因為美國d左膠民眾唔鍾意 就會唔制衡中國呀 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係唔會呀! 佢仲會幫你兜點解會咁樣</span></span> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kuYVC2F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkuYVC2F.jpg&h=9ae127ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反而呢度班仆街左膠 一日到黑係度開d 垃圾 post <br />\n又話勇武呢樣唔岩果樣唔岩 衝入立法會又話唔岩 爆鐵又話唔岩 爆美心又話唔岩 係度帶風向 屌手足<br />\n你地問心 勇武手足做既野有冇令我地失望過? <br />\n612 阻到惡法立法會二讀 701 入左立法會宣讀宣言 仲有之後無數次保護大家免受黑社會福建幫既恐嚇<br />\n你班仆街情願聽冷氣左膠軍師係度講去屌尻勇武手足? <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇良知呀你地</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n裝修唔差十日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1628717/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1628717/page/1</a><br />\nsoloman yue 俾美國人質緊因為勇武燒野而應唔應該繼續推動法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1628983/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1628983/page/1</a><br />\n我個美國Friend尋晚揸緊車...<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1628112/page/54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1628112/page/54</a><br />\n<br />\n你班仆街仲要幫佢推post 俾like?<br />\n你地知唔知停曬做呢d野 就係向世界發出呢個香港人妥協左既信息 俾黑狗進行大搜捕 送我地既勇武手足去死<br />\n為左俾你地班撚屌係度呃like 叫我地手足坐係屋企等差佬上門大搜捕 拉返狗屋 毒打 強姦 輪姦 雞姦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌曬你地老母!</span><br />\n左膠個目的就係為左幫政府平亂 搞死場運動 同差佬一樣要死全家<br />\n<br />\n俾like d 左膠撚屌post之前唔該你地睇下呢條片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZubvzTs9uJ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZubvzTs9uJ4&d=zkxump%2FGNOlz%2FwmZAqM4lITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=161537ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZubvzTs9uJ4</a>"},{"pid":"642726efc0fdb3b209c932181114b577d4340543","tid":1629380,"uid":59753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:33:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"418b64fc279cbd70d41c50a7880ab5da6d7d6b12","tid":1629380,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gsPBnOa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgsPBnOa.jpg&h=db8b2369&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa190a1941f4130e2d5379f6ff240440c120672f","tid":1629380,"uid":103842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:57:56.000Z","msg":"屌你老母仲係見到一堆垃圾左膠屌手足"},{"pid":"9e3899c798a25792c4390aa555f93bd1553631cc","tid":1629380,"uid":2883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:59:49.000Z","msg":"班左膠根本係共犯黎"},{"pid":"2469078da9cf104ad86c9c143c245a07de526f08","tid":1629380,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:01:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83deab153edd532ef8f5c71f2cd35aef5f681110","tid":1629380,"uid":103842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:07:55.000Z","msg":"今晚唔要再見到撚屌左膠POST 有過千LIKE"},{"pid":"dfdf198191e2b85a6cab9b8f6fcec8467afc3e4d","tid":1629380,"uid":103842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score